    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variable  grayish color resembling the color of the sky and surroundings at dawn, the time when the day begins to grow light as the sun rises.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指各種灰色色彩，近似於黎明時天空和環境的顏色。黎明即太陽升起、天色轉亮的時刻。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variabele grijsachtige kleur die lijkt op de kleur van de lucht en de omgeving bij dageraad, de tijd van de dag dat het licht wordt door de zonsopgang.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cor acinzentada variável que lembra a cor do céu e dos arredores ao amanhecer, momento em que o dia começa a clarear à medida que o sol nasce.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
